title: Primal
description:
1-3. Egg or Chicken?
4. S.M.L
5. Kyou koso, Kitto... (Today, surely...)
6. Kiss Manjuu (Steamed Bun Kiss)
7. Kikimimi ~Risou no Kanojo~ (The Ideal Girlfriend)

Tankoubon version has a couple of extra pages in chapter 1-2-3 (Egg or Chicken) but unfortunately there's only Spanish translation available so I had to use machine translator. I made sure to capture the dialogue properly though and most of it are just an extra sex scene so I hope it's not affecting the original story.

Prologue and extra pages translated by "Gokiburi, NTINFS"
